rooms.name: ITS Help Desk
rooms.HTMLdescrip:
The ITS Help Desk has experienced, qualified staff and extensive facilities with which to diagnose and correct many computer problems. Walk-in, call-in, and email-in service is available for Canisius College students, faculty, and staff. Most problems can be handled directly by the Help Desk. Those requiring further assistance will be assigned to ITS staff for follow-up.

Click here for more information.

rooms.name: Rev. J. Clayton Murray, S.J. Archives
rooms.HTMLdescrip: The Rev. J. Clayton Murray, S.J. Archives serves as the institutional memory of the college. We indentify, acquire and maintain historic records that chronicle the development of the College. Archives ensures an accurate, well- maintained record of decisions which have shaped Canisius College.
